aott/analysis/escape_analysis/stack_allocation.runa  
Stack Allocation Optimization Module for AOTT Memory Management

This module provides stack allocation optimization for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Stack allocatable object identification
- Stack frame layout optimization
- Stack allocation safety verification
- Stack space estimation
- Object lifetime analysis for stack
- Stack allocation code generation
- Stack overflow prevention
- Hybrid stack-heap allocation
- Stack allocation profitability analysis
- Thread-local stack allocation
- Stack allocation for closures
- Escape analysis integration
- Stack unwinding support
- Debug information for stack objects
- Stack allocation statistics tracking
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

